
2. verify if a point is inside a triangle 

(the triangle's edges are not guaranteed to be in counter-clockwise order)

outputs =  BORDER, OUTSIDE, INSIDE

**requirements**
language: C++ (any) 
OS: ubuntu 18.04
compiler: g++ v 7.4.0 (lower version is also fine)

**compile with**
```
g++ -I. main.cpp   # will output a.out
```

**launch with**
```
cat data_short.txt | ./a.out 
cat data_long.txt | ./a.out
```
